{"tid":148422,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"我為左鄭恩地本寫真同男朋友分手","createTime":"2017-03-08T14:57:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-15T11:58:18.000Z","uid":80183,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"eb34219b25f0c8910abd1380e45125965d25beca","tid":148422,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T14:57:31.000Z","msg":"上個禮拜我男朋友拎住份蘋果同我講,<br />\n人地鄭恩地好身材, D雪糕滴滴下正到痺,<br />\n我好嬲, 就發火鬧佢, 我係無身材啊, 咁又點?<br />\n尋晚俾我發現, 佢條友靜靜雞走去左信和買鄭恩地本寫真,<br />\n仲收收埋埋係個廁所既化妝櫃度, 上面黃gum gum成攤跡,<br />\n我問佢係咪拎黎攪過, 佢死口話排隊買寫真果陣整污糟,<br />\n算啦, 廿幾歲人成個初中生咁, 淨係識睇樣睇身材,<br />\n寧願對住個韓國妹攪, 咁叻返去食雪糕啦, 分手吧<br />\n條友仲日日打電話黎煩, 激死我喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d71cd3a0f559e39f2de13424652f86e947b3b41","tid":148422,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T14:59:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fbefb9610d08639b266171a578246e33979c7667","tid":148422,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T15:01:03.000Z","msg":"g"},{"pid":"e1581f809aa40df3c842fa421ed0bb84d695c22b","tid":148422,"uid":43979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T15:03:58.000Z","msg":"收皮啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"256e638939ae09d032110af3304dc306c8a6693b","tid":148422,"uid":80183,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T15:05:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9V1215Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9V1215Q.jpg&h=7cc0f0f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲係到扮天真純情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1559c05425e47a501f900aaec35ade3d30ce94c","tid":148422,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T15:05:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>收皮啦屌你老母</blockquote><br />\n咩料呀＝＝？"},{"pid":"7c74018e18b97d4a90f51f2bbfd589ccc4f0ca8f","tid":148422,"uid":43979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T15:06:35.000Z","msg":"<blockq